WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.180 --> 00:00:05.179
Don't worry. It's good news. Your mom is showing signs of regaining consciousness.

2
00:00:05.179 --> 00:00:08.179
That's amazing. God, thank you so much.

3
00:00:08.179 --> 00:00:12.179
I've already taken care of your medical expenses. So don't worry about that.

4
00:00:12.179 --> 00:00:16.500
Thank you, Dexter. I really, really, really mean it.

5
00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:23.019
Hello? Is this St. Joseph's Hospital?

6
00:00:23.019 --> 00:00:28.019
I'm calling regarding my mother, Mary Spencer. I need her medical bill.

7
00:00:28.019 --> 00:00:36.939
You can do this.

8
00:00:36.939 --> 00:00:41.939
Get it together. Your mom really needs you. She's in the hospital and you need to cover her bills.

9
00:00:41.939 --> 00:00:51.670
So stop thinking about him.

10
00:00:51.670 --> 00:01:04.239
I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry.

11
00:01:04.239 --> 00:01:07.239
You're hurt. Let me take you to the hospital.

12
00:01:07.239 --> 00:01:10.239
Oh, it's okay. I live nearby for some medicine.

13
00:01:10.239 --> 00:01:16.480
Well, Mary, let me give my jacket.

14
00:01:16.480 --> 00:01:19.090
Thank you.

